author: woonsan
msg: [JS2-791] configure the security constraint on a particular portlet fragment.
Fixed the problem: failing to seed data because PropertyPlaceholderConfigurer fails to load property variable defined in registry.xml.
This problem was a side-effect of my previous patch (http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?rev=593513&view=rev).
The seed-registry.xml is now used for seeding data and it does not use PropertyPlaceholderConfigurer.
